<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Faculty Recruitment Portal - Closed</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-image: url('<%= asset_path "NITK_Lighthouse.jpg" %>');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            position: relative;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); /* Increased transparency */
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }
        p {
            color: #34495e;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 4em;
            color: #3498db;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        #logo_div {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        #logo_div img {
            max-width: 100px;
            height: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon"></div>
        <h1>Faculty Recruitment Portal is closed</h1>
        <%# <p>Faculty Recruitment Portal is now closed.</p> %>
        <p>Deadline to recieve printed applications is 5pm, 23-Aug-2024.</p>
        <div class="footer">

        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>